Will you play a druid? <p>Dimentox Stormbringer
</p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#f7f5e6><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title><A HREF="http://www.ezboard.com/promotions/csc.html" TARGET="_blank" ><IMG SRC="http://www.ezboard.com/image/cscicon.gif" WIDTH="20" HEIGHT="20" BORDER="0" align="absmiddle"></A> <A HREF=http://pub13.ezboard.com/uginwen.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Ginwen</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#333399>(6/8/01 6:59:53 am)</font><br>     <br>Community Supporter<br> </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: With the New Server Up....</span><hr size=1> New server sounds cool.  Not cool enough to get me to get readdicted to Evercrack, mind you, but pretty cool nonetheless.  A lot of good features (at least on test) that seem to make it much more of a role-playing game (without forcing you to say thee and thou all the time). <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#e6ebd7><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub13.ezboard.com/udimentox.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Dimentox</A>&nbsp; <IMG SRC=http://www.ezboard.com/ezgfx/gicons/anim_1.gif BORDER=0></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#333399>(6/8/01 7:09:30 am)</font><br>    <BR><img src=http://www.gothic-net.com/gothic2.gif WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: With the New Server Up....</span><hr size=1> When they did the talons and vallons alot of people thought that would bring more role playing into it... The fact is that its very hard with an item driven and level driven game to be productive twards roleplaying .. I wouls like to see a RP only server actually...<br>
 <p>Dimentox Stormbringer
</p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#f7f5e6><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title><A HREF="http://www.ezboard.com/promotions/csc.html" TARGET="_blank" ><IMG SRC="http://www.ezboard.com/image/cscicon2.gif" WIDTH="20" HEIGHT="20" BORDER="0" align="absmiddle"></A> <A HREF=http://pub13.ezboard.com/udaeddwin.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Daeddwin</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#333399>(6/8/01 8:34:58 am)</font><br>     <br>Community Supporter<br> </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: With the New Server Up....</span><hr size=1> My big concern is the &quot;Anything Goes&quot; attitude towards PvP on the new server.  I play on a blue server, and the thought of a level 50 or 60 griefer offing me for no reason, and having no recourse to it... it makes me a lot less prone to play.  If the PvP rules were more in line with the PvP teams server, I'd be a lot more interested.<br>
<br>
 <p>Daeddwin Proudfoot<br>
37th (FINALLY) Level Lowbie Halfling Druid<br>
Officer of <i>Spirit of Norrath</i><br>
<b>Lanys T'yvl</b></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#e6ebd7><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title><A HREF="http://www.ezboard.com/promotions/csc.html" TARGET="_blank" ><IMG SRC="http://www.ezboard.com/image/cscicon.gif" WIDTH="20" HEIGHT="20" BORDER="0" align="absmiddle"></A> <A HREF=http://pub13.ezboard.com/uginwen.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Ginwen</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#333399>(6/8/01 9:12:41 am)</font><br>     <br>Community Supporter<br> </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: With the New Server Up....</span><hr size=1> Off the top of my head, the things I liked, and that I thought at least sort of encouraged role playing, were the one character allowed on the server (per account, of course, and since an awful lot of people have multiple accounts...), and the fact that you couldn't guild with or cast beneficial spells on members of the other teams.<br>
<br>
I think it would be good, as far as the faction hits for killing someone in their home town if your faction was only hurt by killing someone in their home town if you initiated the attack, but that might be hard to code (or at least, hurt less if you were just defending yourself).  That way, if I wanted to, for example, work on my faction to the point that I could visit the ogre city with my wood elf druid, that wouldn't be ruined by some schmuck attacking me (or alternatively, I wouldn't have to let them kill me so that my faction wouldn't be messed up).<br>
<br>
The whole PvP thing I don't much care for, but I'd like to see some of the other features carried over to some of the other servers. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#f7f5e6><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub13.ezboard.com/bthedruidsgrove.showLocalUserPublicProfile?login=rtfm>rtfm</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#333399>(6/8/01 9:13:48 am)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: With the New Server Up....</span><hr size=1> &quot;having no recourse to it&quot;<br>
<br>
You have a lot of recourses, you just need to be creative.<br>
<br>
Being on a blue server *truely* offers no recourse to griefers and harrassment. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#e6ebd7><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub13.ezboard.com/ubraidfreak.showPublicProfile?language=EN>braidfreak</A>&nbsp; <IMG SRC=http://www.ezboard.com/ezgfx/gicons/anim_1.gif BORDER=0></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#333399>(6/10/01 12:33:31 pm)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: With the New Server Up....</span><hr size=1> i got my shammy ogre up to level 10 and now i'm bored.  <br>
<br>
there was only 2 other people in oasis.<br>
<br>
i ran around uninhibited through east commons.<br>
<br>
every time i run up to someone, they turn tail and run away.  they don't even take the time to /con me, as most of them are on my team anyways.<br>
<br>
sheesh, it's a friggin PvP server and no one wants to fight.  so now i'm bored with it.  i already trivialed out with patchwork armor.  i already got sow.  now i'm just bored. <p>check out simplekill...a band that's about to explode and squash queer bands like korn
http://www.simplekill.net</p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#f7f5e6><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title><A HREF="http://www.ezboard.com/promotions/csc.html" TARGET="_blank" ><IMG SRC="http://www.ezboard.com/image/cscicon.gif" WIDTH="20" HEIGHT="20" BORDER="0" align="absmiddle"></A> <A HREF=http://pub13.ezboard.com/uyanguboris.showPublicProfile?language=EN>YanguBoris</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#333399>(6/10/01 1:03:54 pm)</font><br>     <br>Community Supporter<br> </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: With the New Server Up....</span><hr size=1> braid, I think not many want to get too far because chars will be wiped soon. When it is released live everyone will be making a beeline for 60 so they can go molest everyone easily =P <p><font face="Tahoma">48 (Indefinitely) Wood Elf Druid, Vazaelle<br>20 Ogre Warrior, Vazaelle<p><i>"We are all born mad. Some remain so."</i></font></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#e6ebd7><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub13.ezboard.com/uraddruid.showPublicProfile?language=EN>RadDruid</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#333399>(6/11/01 6:37:59 am)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: With the New Server Up....</span><hr size=1> I think I can molest people more effectively as a lvl 5 WElf Bard.  You cant touch me, but I can train you!<br>
I am so glad Verant will have a level range where you are immune to any recourse or responsibility, levels 1-5.<br>
The beauty of this, is that I can prance about the dead corpses gloating on how they cant touch me when they come back to loot(or with their friends).<br>
<br>
&lt;sarcasm off&gt;<br>
<br>
Only allowing one character per account for the new server is a great start, but having this perm aura of invulnerability for level 1-5's is like giving a loaded gun(painted orange) to child and telling him/her its a new super soaker.  Alot of people have two accounts.<br>
<br>
-Radagorn<br>
 <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#f7f5e6><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub13.ezboard.com/umylo.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Mylo</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#333399>(6/11/01 6:41:55 am)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: With the New Server Up....</span><hr size=1> You know the fun thing about the new server?  You get to start over at level 1. <p>"Clarity can be attained solely through the purgery of hatred."

-Mylo Modisto 
(level 59 Wood Elf Preserver of Xegony)</p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#e6ebd7><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub13.ezboard.com/ubraidfreak.showPublicProfile?language=EN>braidfreak</A>&nbsp; <IMG SRC=http://www.ezboard.com/ezgfx/gicons/anim_1.gif BORDER=0></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#333399>(6/11/01 10:33:03 am)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: With the New Server Up....</span><hr size=1> ya, i know we're all gonna get whiped, so why be afraid to fight?  you're gonna be deleted anyways.  i'd think peple would be more apt to fight since their characters don't mean anything. :)<br>
<br>
ah well, about a week into it and still can't find anyone to fight me. <p>check out simplekill...a band that's about to explode and squash queer bands like korn
